Simple python script to monitor External IP address of Dev Server and send direct message tweet if it changes

To use script, please  add Twitter credentials as environment variables
1. twitter_consumer_key
2. twitter_consumer_secret
3. twitter_access_token_key
4. twitter_access_token_secret
5. twitter_screen_name

Improvements needed:
Enable cron jobs to check for IP changes every 30 minutes
Enable cron job to start up upon restart

Usage: python whatsmyipaddress.py
